metadata.name: PANIK AT THE DINER
metadata.description:
"Panik at the Diner"

Everything's going according to plan until your brain wanders off, way off. You shouldn't be thinking about any of this right now. "No...no, no, no no no! What the f*ck is wrong with you?!"

It's your moment, waiting to be seized but suddenly you can tell you're running out of air, forgetting how to breathe. The party's waiting for you inside as you sit bare and paralyzed, thoughts consuming you.

''Maybe I shouldn't have said that.. What will they think? Who am I? Why am I here? If I can catch that one breath again, will I have the answers then?''

'I know I have to try no matter what.'

Breathe. We'll make it out of this.
